The paper focuses on exploring privacy threats stemming from large language models (LLMs), particularly OpenAI’s ChatGPT and the New Bing, an integration enhanced by ChatGPT. The main contributions of the paper lie in conducting a thorough privacy analysis of these advanced LLMs, showcasing how application-integrated LLMs can introduce new privacy vulnerabilities.
